Male Merchant: The fun is just beginning, but hey, keep

events.name: 華麗なるギャンブラー1-3

parameters:
Miner Man: W-Who the hell are you guys?! If you don't want
to be violated, get the hell out of here!

Fuego the Hawk's Eye: That's quite a spirited greeting. If
that's the case, I would have liked to receive a greeting
from our organization.

Fuego the Hawk's Eye: So you're saying there's gambling
going on here?

Miner Man: W-Well...heheh! There are only four women here,
including you.

Miner Man: Even if there are many people, the advantage is
still on our side--

Fuego the Hawk's Eye: You know about the miraculous victory
achieved by the four beautiful goddesses who defeated the
undefeated Iron Mask, right?

Fuego the Hawk's Eye: If we're going to fight, I'll step
aside. I don't want to stain my clothes with your blood, you
see.

Miner Man: W-Wait! We'll pay the tribute from now on, so
please spare us!

Fuego the Hawk's Eye: From now on...? I will be satisfied
with the past and the future.
Miner Man: Alright... I'll prepare the money right away.
3.イベント後のプレイヤーの位置
